        public final long cachedDataLength()
        Description copied from interface: StorageEntity
        The length this entity occupies in the cache. This might be vary, even for fixed length typed, from the values returned by StorageEntity.dataLength() as only parts of an entity (e.g. only references) might be loaded into cache and because the cache might hold the header/meta data of an entity as well.
